21110/「可不可以陪我」12歲女LINE揪狼爸">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;「可不可以陪我」12歲女LINE揪狼爸</option><option value="/appledaily/article/headline/20141002/36121112/夜店殺警案薛貞國告別式">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;夜店殺警案薛貞國告別式</option><option value="/appledaily/article/headline/20141002/36121115/港警動用「香蕉水」?!藍委質詢口誤糗爆了">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;港警動用「香蕉水」?! 藍委質詢口誤 糗爆了</option></optgroup><optgroup label="論壇"><option value="/appledaily/article/headline/20141002/36120981/傳承與前瞻：催淚彈與想飛的自由（施明德）">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;傳承與前瞻：催淚彈與想飛的自由（施明德）</option><option value="/appledaily/article/headline/20141002/36120987/那我不認識的香港抗爭者（陳中寧）">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;那我不認識的香港抗爭者（陳中寧）</option><option value="/appledaily/article/headline/20141002/36120991/港警侵害醫療人權（黃峻偉）">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;港警侵害醫療人權（黃峻偉）</option><option value="/appledaily/article/headline/20141002/36120995/蘋中信：梁振英的兩顆子彈（王尚智）">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;蘋中信：梁振英的兩顆子彈（王尚智）</option><option value="/appledaily/article/headline/20141002/36121001/負擔不起的慾望城市（夏綠蒂）">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;負擔不起的慾望城市（夏綠蒂）</option><option value="/appledaily/article/headline/20141002/36119082/人間異語：兒子的心肝在你身上可安好">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;人間異語：兒子的心肝 在你身上可安好</option><option value="/appledaily/article/headline/20141002/36121005/新聞魔法">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;新聞魔法</option><option value="/appledaily/article/headline/20141002/36121008/每日一短蘋">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;每日一短蘋</option><option value="/appledaily/article/headline/20141002/36121010/《蘋果論壇》徵稿">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;《蘋果論壇》徵稿</option></optgroup><optgroup label="法庭"><option value="/appledaily/article/headline/20141002/36120420/餵毒性侵小姊妹狼爺判42年">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;餵毒性侵小姊妹 狼爺判42年</option><option value="/appledaily/article/headline/20141002/36120427/李宗瑞前女友販毒假釋將出監">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;李宗瑞前女友 販毒假釋將出監</option><option value="/appledaily/article/headline/20141002/36120430/創投教父炒股更一審仍判9年">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;創投教父炒股 更一審仍判9年</option><option value="/appledaily/article/